13
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:14,900
So beautiful!

14
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:16,780
Every day from now on,

15
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:19,260
you'll enjoy with me

16
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:21,860
the full-blown flowers

17
