82
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,180
Can't you

83
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,980
feel my heart?

84
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,300
In my heart,

85
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,580
